title: Welcome to JulSwap Voting!
body:
JulSwap Voting page is created.

Everyone can create proposal for review from other users.
While proposal active time, users can vote him without any gas fee, only signing his account will be enough.
More JULb owners will have a greater impact on Proposal's final execution.

Please create more effective and more progressive proposals for our JulSwap.

JulSwap team.
